---
title: Italian Sausage Rigatoni Includes recyclable aluminum tray
description: This pasta bake keeps cleanup to a minimum thanks to our oven-ready tray. Fresh rigatoni cooks up perfectly tender in the oven along with our flavorful Italian pork sausage, peas, and a rich tomato-pepper sauce (aka romesco!)—with no prep required. Finish it with a sprinkle of nutty Parmesan for a convenient, delicious meal in a flash!
